<lb n="0032a14"/><p><note place="inline">癸未</note>更始元<note place="inline">劉玄字聖公。滅莽治<anchor id="fnT49p0032a20"/>二年。為赤眉所殺。<anchor id="fnT49p0032a21"/>玄景帝<anchor id="fnT49p0032a22"/>六世孫。<anchor id="fnT49p0032a23"/>佛入涅槃<anchor id="fnT49p0032a24"/>至此六百三十二年</note>　<note place="inline">甲申</note>二</p>
