<lb n="0032a22"/>禪梁甫訖<anchor id="fnT49p0032a31"/>迴。過魯祠孔子宅。九月醴泉出。京師飲者痼疾皆<anchor id="fnT49p0032a32"/>差也</note>　<note place="inline">丁巳</note>二<note place="inline">是歲取天下民戶凡四百二十七萬九千六百<anchor id="fnT49p0032a33"/>四十四民口二千一百萬七千八百二十</note></p>
<lb n="0032a23"/><p><note place="inline">戊午</note>明帝莊<note place="inline">光武第<anchor id="fnT49p0032a34"/>四子立十八年<anchor id="fnT49p0032a35"/>號永平元。<anchor id="fnT49p0032a36"/>佛入涅槃至此<anchor id="fnT49p0032a37"/>已六百六十七年</note>　<note place="inline">己未</note>二　<note place="inline">庚申</note>三　<note place="inline">辛酉</note>四
<lb n="0032a24"/>　<note place="inline">壬戌</note>五　<note place="inline">癸亥</note>六　<note place="inline">甲子</note>七<note place="inline">是年帝夢金人飛來殿庭。<anchor id="fnT49p0032a38"/>即佛像經法應也。命使西行尋求佛經</note>　<note place="inline">乙丑</note>八
