<lb n="0059a27"/><p>菩薩二百五十法經<anchor id="fnT49p0059a10"/>一卷<note place="inline">或<anchor id="fnT49p0059a11"/>二卷。<anchor id="fnT49p0059a12"/>以此代僧<anchor id="fnT49p0059a13"/>二百五十戒呈皓
<pb ed="T" id="T49.2034.0059b" n="0059b"/>
<lb n="0059b01"/>者是</note></p>
