<lb n="0064b19"/><p>多聞經一卷<note place="inline">已下<anchor id="fnT49p0064b12"/>四十八部四十八卷。並是<anchor id="fnT49p0064b13"/>見吳錄別錄及晉世<anchor id="fnT49p0064b14"/>別錄</note></p>
